wiki.content: Following the radio and chart smash 'Bounce' feat. Kelis, Calvin's catchy follow-up solo single 'Feel So Close' stormed to No.2 in the UK chart in late August 2011. Calvin has been keeping exceptionally busy with DJ residences across the globe and is currently on a huge tour of the UK and Europe with Rihanna.
